Question 1.4

salmon_tibble <- as_tibble(transformed_salmon, rownames=NA)

top100var <- salmon_tibble %>% rownames_to_column() %>% rowwise() %>% 
  mutate(variance=var(c(WT1, WT2, WT3, WTTPA1, WTTPA2, WTTPA3))) %>% 
  arrange(desc(variance)) %>% slice(1:100)
